textDelta: There are real, and valuable prizes for winning in life
Life has rules that everyone is supposed to follow
There is no handy instruction booklet for life, you have to figure out the rules as you go
Most people agree on the desired outcome of life, but everyone decides on their own strategy of how to reach that goal.
Life is meant to be enjoyed, and most people would agree that they had fun while living it.
People sometimes cheat in life, even when the stakes are low
Some people put too much emphasis on winning in life, and forget to enjoy it for what it is
Building up a strong team can help you to win in life.

textDelta: When you reach the last inning in life, you might be so far ahead that you don't need to keep struggling, or so far behind that you might as well relax.
Money, power, and respect can be thought of as points on the scoreboard of life
In life, you have to deal with the cards that you were dealt at the beginning
Sometimes you just have to roll the dice and hope for the best.
Life has its winners and its losers, but no one wants you to give up and stop trying to play

textDelta: As the old saying goes, sometimes the way you play is more important than whether you win or lose
People respect a player who acts graciously, whether he or she is winning or losing
Life is not always a zero-sum game, you can win by helping others, and your success does not have to mean that someone else loses.
